---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy — OmniBrand">
  <Header />
  <main>
    <section class="privacy-policy section">
      <div class="privacy-policy__header">
        <div class="container">
          <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
          <p class="privacy-policy__subtitle">We care about keeping your data safe</p>
          <p class="privacy-policy__updated">Last Updated: 22/02/2024</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="container">
        <div class="privacy-policy__content">
          <p>Thank you for visiting our website. Your privacy is important to us, and we are committed to protecting any personal information you share with us. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your information.</p>

          <h2>1. Who We Are</h2>
          <p>We are a New Zealand-based company providing branding and design-related services. While we are not regulated by the United States or European privacy laws, we recognize that some of our customers may be from these regions.</p>

          <h2>2. What Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>We collect the following types of information:</p>

          <h3>Website Analytics</h3>
          <p>We use Google Analytics to gather insights about visitor behavior on our site.</p>
          <p>We use Microsoft Clarity for advanced behavior metrics, such as heat mapping and session replay.</p>

          <h3>Booking Information</h3>
          <p>We use an embedded Calendly form to allow visitors to book meetings with our team. When booking, users provide their name and contact details.</p>

          <h3>Service-Related Information</h3>
          <p>When purchasing our services, we collect necessary details such as name, email, and service requirements to provide branding and design-related services.</p>
          <p>We accept credit card payments through our forms.</p>

          <h3>Contact Forms</h3>
          <p>When reaching out through our contact forms, we may collect:</p>
          <ul class="privacy-policy__list">
            <li>Name</li>
            <li>Email address</li>
            <li>Information about the services you are interested in</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>We use your information to:</p>
          <ul class="privacy-policy__list">
            <li>Provide and improve our services.</li>
            <li>Respond to inquiries and customer service requests.</li>
            <li>Process payments for services.</li>
            <li>Understand user behavior through analytics.</li>
            <li>Schedule meetings efficiently.</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>4. How We Protect Your Information</h2>
          <p>We take data security seriously and implement reasonable measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, loss, or misuse. We do not sell or share your information with third parties.</p>

          <h2>5. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p>We use third-party services, such as Google Analytics, Microsoft Clarity, and Calendly, which may collect and process data according to their privacy policies. We recommend reviewing their respective policies for further details:</p>
          <ul class="privacy-policy__list">
            <li><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">Google Analytics Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://clarity.microsoft.com/privacy" target="_blank">Microsoft Clarity Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://calendly.com/privacy" target="_blank">Calendly Privacy Policy</a></li>
          </ul>

          <h2>6. Your Rights & Choices</h2>
          <p>You have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="privacy-policy__list">
            <li>Request access to the personal data we hold about you.</li>
            <li>Request corrections or deletion of your information.</li>
            <li>Opt-out of analytics tracking via browser settings or Google's opt-out tools.</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with the updated date.</p>

          <p>If you have any questions, please reach out to us at <a href="mailto:support@omnibrand.co.nz">support@omnibrand.co.nz</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .privacy-policy {
    padding-block: 0 var(--space-lg);
  }

  .privacy-policy__header {
    text-align: center;
    background-color: var(--color-deep-teal);
    color: var(--color-white);
    padding: var(--space-2xl) 0;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
    width: 100vw;
    margin-left: calc(-50vw + 50%);
  }

  .privacy-policy__header h1 {
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .privacy-policy__subtitle {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--color-off-white);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .privacy-policy__updated {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-mid-grey);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .privacy-policy__content {
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .privacy-policy__content p {
    margin-inline: 0;
    max-width: none;
  }

  .privacy-policy__content h2 {
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .privacy-policy__content h3 {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .privacy-policy__content p {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .privacy-policy__list {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .privacy-policy__list li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .privacy-policy__content a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
    transition: color var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .privacy-policy__content a:hover {
    color: var(--color-berry-light);
  }
</style>
